---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';

const lastUpdated = 'July 2026';
---

<Layout
  title="Terms of Use | NM Nonprofits"
  description="Terms of use for NM Nonprofits: the New Mexico nonprofit and funder directory."
>
  <div class="container-content py-16 max-w-3xl">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-serif font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Terms of Use</h1>
    <p class="text-gray-400 text-sm mb-12">Last updated: {lastUpdated}</p>

    <div class="space-y-10 text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Acceptance of terms</h2>
        <p>
          By accessing or using nmnonprofits.com ("the Site"), you agree to these Terms of Use. If you do not agree, please do not use the Site. We may update these terms at any time; continued use after changes constitutes acceptance.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">About the directory</h2>
        <p>
          NM Nonprofits is an independent directory of New Mexico nonprofit organizations, foundations, and funders. We are not affiliated with any listed organization, the IRS, the New Mexico Secretary of State, or any government agency. Listing information is compiled from public records and direct submissions and is provided for informational purposes only.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Accuracy of information</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          We make reasonable efforts to keep directory information accurate and current, but we do not guarantee the completeness, accuracy, or timeliness of any listing. Organization details including contact information, mission statements, and financial data may be out of date.
        </p>
        <p>
          Grant and funding information is time-sensitive. Always verify deadlines, eligibility requirements, and award amounts directly with the funder before applying. NM Nonprofits is not responsible for missed deadlines or inaccurate grant information.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Submitting listings</h2>
        <p class="mb-4">
          Organizations may submit or update their own listing through the Site. By submitting information you represent that you are authorized to do so on behalf of the organization and that the information provided is accurate.
        </p>
        <p>
          We reserve the right to approve, edit, decline, or remove any listing at our discretion. Submissions that contain false information, violate applicable law, or are otherwise inappropriate will be rejected or removed.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Intellectual property</h2>
        <p>
          The design, layout, and original content of this Site are owned by NM Nonprofits. Directory data sourced from public records is not subject to our copyright. You may not reproduce, republish, or resell this directory's contents in bulk or as a competing product without written permission.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Affiliate links</h2>
        <p>
          Some links on this Site, including book recommendations in our Guides section, are Amazon affiliate links. As an Amazon Associate, NM Nonprofits earns a small commission on qualifying purchases at no additional cost to you. Affiliate links are marked with <code class="bg-gray-100 px-1 py-0.5 rounded text-sm">rel="sponsored"</code> and do not influence editorial recommendations.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Advertising</h2>
        <p>
          This Site displays advertisements served by Google AdSense. Ad content is controlled by Google and its partners based on contextual signals and, where applicable, your interests and browsing history. NM Nonprofits does not endorse advertised products or services. See our <a href="/privacy/" class="text-turquoise-700 hover:underline">Privacy Policy</a> for more on how advertising cookies work.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Disclaimer of warranties</h2>
        <p>
          The Site is provided "as is" without warranties of any kind, express or implied. We do not warrant that the Site will be uninterrupted, error-free, or free of viruses or other harmful components. Use of the Site is at your own risk.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Limitation of liability</h2>
        <p>
          To the maximum extent permitted by law, NM Nonprofits shall not be liable for any indirect, incidental, special, or consequential damages arising from your use of the Site or reliance on information contained herein, even if we have been advised of the possibility of such damages.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Governing law</h2>
        <p>
          These terms are governed by the laws of the State of New Mexico, without regard to conflict of law principles.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section>
        <h2 class="text-xl font-serif font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-3">Contact</h2>
        <p>
          Questions about these terms: <a href="mailto:hello@nmnonprofits.com" class="text-turquoise-700 hover:underline">hello@nmnonprofits.com</a>
        </p>
      </section>

    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
